OL,3,CLeicester City helicopter crash which
OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,FThe deaths of former Leicester City
OL,7,Fowner and four others who were killed
OL,8,Fwhen a helicopter crashed outside the
OL,9,FKing Power Stadium and became engulfed
OL,10,Fin flames were accidental, an inquest
OL,11,Fjury has concluded.
OL,13,FVichai Srivaddhanaprabha, referred to
OL,14,Fin court as Khun Vichai, died when the
OL,15,Faircraft crashed and caught on fire,
OL,16,Falso killing the pilot Eric Swaffer,
OL,17,Fhis partner Izabela Lechowicz, and
OL,18,Fpassengers Nusara Suknamai and
OL,19,FKaveporn Punpare.
