OL,6,FMs Mason said: "Five innocent lives
OL,7,Fwere cruelly lost on October 27 2018,
OL,8,Flives that were cut too short.
OL,10,F"This huge loss will be borne by the
OL,11,Ffamilies for the rest of their lives,
OL,12,Fa loss that is also felt by the
OL,13,Fcommunity of Leicester.
OL,15,F"It has been a long journey. Just over
OL,16,Fsix years for you, the families, to
OL,17,Fget the answers you wanted as to how
OL,18,Fyour loved ones came by their deaths.
OL,20,F"I hope you feel through these
OL,21,Finquests that you now have a voice."
