OL,3,CLeicester City helicopter crash which
OL,4,Ckilled five people ruled accidental
OL,6,FThe Leonardo AW169 helicopter
OL,7,F"aggressively" spun out of control
OL,8,Ffrom a height of 430ft and became
OL,9,F"engulfed" in flames while taking off
OL,10,Ffrom the pitch after a match in
OL,11,FLeicester on 27 October 2018.
OL,13,FA report which was published by the
OL,14,FAir Accident Investigation Branch
OL,15,Flooking into the incident in 2023,
OL,16,Fdescribed it as a "tragic accident".
OL,18,FIt revealed the seizure of the tail
OL,19,Frotor duplex bearing initiated a
OL,20,Fsequence of failures. It culminated in
OL,21,Fthe unrecoverable loss of control.
