OL,6,FThe 11 jurors had to answer four
OL,7,Fquestions: who was each deceased
OL,8,Fperson, when did they die, where did
OL,9,Fthey die, and how did they come by
OL,10,Ftheir death.
OL,12,FSenior coroner Catherine Mason had
OL,13,Ftold the jury they should "accept and
OL,14,Ffollow" the findings of the Air
OL,15,FAccidents Investigation Branch (AAIB)
OL,16,Finvestigation into the crash,
OL,17,Fincluding that the pilot's actions
OL,18,Fwere "appropriate and did not
OL,19,Fcontribute to the loss of control".
