OL,6,FThe jury also heard a statement from
OL,7,FKhun Vichai's son, Aiyawatt
OL,8,FSrivaddhanaprabha, which said the
OL,9,Fhelicopter was bought for 7.5 million
OL,10,Feuros and had been maintained by
OL,11,FSloane Helicopters since February 2017.
OL,13,FThe aircraft had one of its bi-monthly
OL,14,F"walk around" checks only 10 days
OL,15,Fbefore the crash.
OL,17,FThe inquest was told the helicopter,
OL,18,Fwhich was considered "in the early
OL,19,Fstages of its life", was manufactured
OL,20,Fin 2016 and had only flown for 330
OL,21,Fhours.
