OL,6,FMs Mason told the jury the pen
OL,7,Fportraits read out on the first day of
OL,8,Fthe inquest were "truly heartbreaking"
OL,9,Fand gave a "glimpse" into the loss
OL,10,Ffelt by their families.
OL,12,FKhun Vichai's family said in his pen
OL,13,Fportrait: "We feel the loss of him as
OL,14,Fmuch today as we have ever done. He
OL,15,Fwas a good man with a good heart. He
OL,16,Fwas a great inspiration to us all and
OL,17,Fwe all loved him very much."
